{"tid":2225123,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【行業辛酸】呢幾個行業輪班制 中秋節無假放？Shift Duty好定壞！","createTime":"2020-10-01T05:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T16:20:55.000Z","uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"473dfeb0d388759130c4bf8f7ae5d6e825fc01d4","tid":2225123,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"中秋節快樂！雖然中秋節是本港法定假期，但依然有好多行業的打工仔，不能在正日當日放假，特別是永遠站在前線的醫護人員，這段時期辛苦你們了！在你們眼中，採用輪班制 (Shift Duty)的又有甚麼行業，他們返晚放早的生活又如何？讓我們一起了解輪班制人員的辛酸吧。<br />\n<br />\n前線記者︰「好耐無同家人正日慶祝」<br />\n前線記者經常早出晚歸，工作不定時，幾乎無機會可以節日的正日放假。現任某傳媒、現入行5年的前線記者阿Bi，接受訪問時表示自從做記者後，甚少可以和家人慶祝節日，她說︰「其實紅假就係得咁多，全組人要輪住正日放假，有幾何可以真係放到，唔好話聖誕、新年，中秋、端午節呢啲節日我都好少機會正日放，見到身邊啲朋友往年成日出街玩，約埋去Party Room、打邊爐咁，次次我都Join唔到，好似無Friend咁&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n保安︰「搵食緊要過慶祝啦」<br />\n至於年過50歲的某屋村叔叔，接受訪問時就話已看開了，他說︰「都咁老啦，慶乜祝呀，求其同屋企人食餐飯咪算囉。而家咁老其實好難搵份工架啦，我求咩？求三餐有得食架咋，其他嘢唔諗啦！」<br />\n<br />\n餐廳侍應︰「其實節日返工仲好」<br />\n在尖沙嘴某餐廳任職侍應的李先生，與之前兩位受訪者的看法截然不同，他認為輪班制比平日朝九晚五好處更多，他說︰「返朝九晚五嗰啲，日日逼車逼到癲，而家我返工嘅時間同一般人唔同，搭車方便好多，講到有冇得放紅假，其實紅假出面人咁多，食飯又要等位，商場又多人，放平日人少啲仲好啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cthr.ctgoodjobs.hk/HRInsight/%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E8%BE%9B%E9%85%B8-%E5%91%A2%E5%B9%BE%E5%80%8B%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E8%BC%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%88%B6-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B%E7%AF%80%E7%84%A1%E5%81%87%E6%94%BE-shift-duty%E5%A5%BD%E5%AE%9A%E5%A3%9E/21877?fbclid=IwAR0cRGYvbofGYseXWd76SrqLuLH9-X614vfiMnB1gbHsSWBvqiZMB4BzG6Q#utm_source=200930_article_legal&amp;utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_campaign=fbpost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcthr.ctgoodjobs.hk%2FHRInsight%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25BE%259B%25E9%2585%25B8-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%258B%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%2594%25BE-shift-duty%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25A3%259E%2F21877%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0cRGYvbofGYseXWd76SrqLuLH9-X614vfiMnB1gbHsSWBvqiZMB4BzG6Q%23utm_source%3D200930_article_legal%26utm_medium%3Dfb%26utm_campaign%3Dfbpost&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w15tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c5d20be4\" target=\"_blank\">https://cthr.ctgoodjobs.hk/HRInsight/%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E8%BE%9B%E9%85%B8-%E5%91%A2%E5%B9%BE%E5%80%8B%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E8%BC%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%88%B6-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%8B%E7%AF%80%E7%84%A1%E5%81%87%E6%94%BE-shift-duty%E5%A5%BD%E5%AE%9A%E5%A3%9E/21877?fbclid=IwAR0cRGYvbofGYseXWd76SrqLuLH9-X614vfiMnB1gbHsSWBvqiZMB4BzG6Q#utm_source=200930_article_legal&amp;utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_campaign=fbpost</a>"},{"pid":"fee7f40f98dffcaa428bd3fe11bcec26a3727c67","tid":2225123,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5011e8f26f89d837ec7a7dcd662ca9516519e84","tid":2225123,"uid":77630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"連登好似冇咩人輪班"},{"pid":"455dbb56a172b95b971b80553e8de5d5bb904ecd","tid":2225123,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"求三餐有得食架咋，其他嘢唔諗啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22a6aaa7041197a9f30f4549519d0876ee77bb7","tid":2225123,"uid":357236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"返夜揮手區👋🏻"},{"pid":"9959af19a8acdce67f852eb5fb6e422a546eb8f0","tid":2225123,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T19:28:04.000Z","msg":"我依啲毒撚其實有興趣嘅無仿"},{"pid":"21ad5e5f8ef3d6573d83d358e0010c6ffe5a2c0b","tid":2225123,"uid":303463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}